<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida7f68da3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s649e"><num value="649e">§ 649e.</num><heading> Promotions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Sections 620 through 626 of this title shall apply in promotions of officers in competitive categories of officers designated for purposes of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida7f68da4-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tV/s507/a/1">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title V, § 507(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1746">132 Stat. 1746</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
